biannual revisions (up or down) under certain conditions, but
are capped at an annual rate of 6.75% (until march12,
2014), 7.625% (until march12, 2022) and 8.50% (until
september12, 2030). as of october1, 2005 the rate on
the subordinated loans was 3.29%.
